{"tha-ap137:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap137:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap137:0.3":"5 Rahosannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap137:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap137:1.2":"vasabho nama pabbato; ","tha-ap137:1.3":"Tasmim pabbatapadamhi, ","tha-ap137:1.4":"assamo asi mapito. ","tha-ap137:2.1":"Tini sissasahassani, ","tha-ap137:2.2":"vacesim brahmano tada; ","tha-ap137:2.3":"Samharitvana te sisse, ","tha-ap137:2.4":"ekamantam upavisim. ","tha-ap137:3.1":"Ekamantam nisiditva, ","tha-ap137:3.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap137:3.3":"Buddhavedam gavesanto, ","tha-ap137:3.4":"nane cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap137:4.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap137:4.2":"nisidim pannasanthare; ","tha-ap137:4.3":"Pallankam abhujitvana, ","tha-ap137:4.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap137:5.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap137:5.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap137:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap137:5.4":"nanasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap137:6.1":"Sattavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap137:6.2":"raja siridharo ahu; ","tha-ap137:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap137:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap137:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap137:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap137:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap137:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma rahosannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap137:9.1":"Rahosannakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}